## Live Demo

You can try the Movie Search App live by visiting the following link:

[Movie Search App Live Demo](https://tekporlipos.github.io/movie-search-web-app/)


## Setup

1. Clone the repository or download the source code.
2. Open the project in your preferred code editor.
3. Ensure you have a stable internet connection.
4. Launch the application by opening the `index.html` file in a web browser.

## Credits

- [OMDB API](http://www.omdbapi.com): The API used for fetching movie data.
- [Glide.js](https://glidejs.com): The library used for creating the carousel of related movies.
- [Swiper.js](https://swiperjs.com): The library used for creating the image carousel in the movie details page.

